name: The Thinky Blinky Monsters2
description: The Thinky Blinky Monsters are a series of randomly generated NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain. The first edition is made up of 20,000 monsters with approximately 350 attributes; each one having to do with their specialty and how they help you. The potential number of unique combinations exceeds 6 billion in total. There is one entirely different "Pa-Ma Monster" who is the parent of all the Thinky Blinky Monsters.
